# name: Demo 08 - always, noninertial i alarm
# description: Wlaczenie przelacznika wymusza light, a light wymusza alarm.

fluents s1, s2, light, alarm
actions toggle1, toggle2
always (s1 or s2) -> light
always light -> alarm
noninertial light
noninertial alarm
initially !s1 and !s2
toggle1 causes s1 if !s1
toggle1 causes !s1 if s1
toggle2 causes s2 if !s2
toggle2 causes !s2 if s2
